seasonal allergies (hay fever),"Oral antihistamines (e.g., Cetirizine) | Intranasal corticosteroids (e.g., Fluticasone) | Leukotriene receptor antagonists (e.g., Montelukast) | Nasal saline rinses | Allergy immunotherapy"
fungal infection of the hair,Griseofulvin (oral) | Terbinafine (oral) | Ketoconazole shampoo | Selenium sulfide shampoo | Itraconazole
