obstructive sleep apnea (osa),"CPAP (Continuous Positive Airway Pressure) | Weight loss | Mandibular advancement device | Modafinil (for residual sleepiness) | Surgery (e.g., UPPP, if indicated)"
psoriasis,"Topical corticosteroids | Vitamin D analogs (e.g., Calcipotriol) | Methotrexate | Biologics (e.g., Adalimumab) | Phototherapy (UVB)"
arthritis of the hip,NSAIDs | Corticosteroid injections | Physical therapy | Glucosamine supplements | Hip replacement surgery (in advanced cases)
sickle cell crisis,"Hydroxyurea | Folic acid | Pain management (e.g., Morphine) | IV fluids | Blood transfusions (if needed)"
otitis externa (swimmer's ear),"Topical antibiotic ear drops (e.g., Ciprofloxacin + Hydrocortisone) | Acidifying drops (e.g., Acetic acid) | Analgesics | Ear wick for deep infections | Avoid water exposure"
acute bronchiolitis,"Supportive care | Nasal suctioning | Saline nebulization | Oxygen therapy (if hypoxic) | Antipyretics (e.g., Paracetamol)"
